graph LR
    RHOAIOperator[RHOAI Operator<br/>rhods-operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    RHOAIOperator -->|orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>REQUIRED]
    RHOAIOperator -->|Routes, OAuth,<br/>ImageStreams| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+<br/>REQUIRED]
    RHOAIOperator -->|ServiceMonitor CRDs| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator 0.69.1<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    RHOAIOperator -.->|TLS certificates<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHOAIOperator -.->|service mesh<br/>required for KServe| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh 2.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHOAIOperator -.->|managed addon<br/>OSD/ROSA only| AddonOperator[Addon Operator<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal RHOAI Components (Deployed/Managed)
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI]
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| KServe[KServe<br/>Single-model serving]
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Multi-model serving]
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow Pipelines]
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>Distributed computing]
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| Ray[Ray<br/>Distributed Python]
    RHOAIOperator -->|deploys| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Jupyter notebooks]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    RHOAIOperator -.->|fetch manifests<br/>devFlags.manifestsUri| GitRepo[Git Repository<br/>OPTIONAL]
    RHOAIOperator -->|pull images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registries<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]

    %% Integration Points
    RHOAIOperator <-->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Primary integration]
    RHOAIOperator -->|register OAuth clients| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    RHOAIOperator -->|metrics| UserWorkloadMon[User Workload Monitoring<br/>Prometheus]
    RHOAIOperator -->|pull images| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry]
    RHOAIOperator -.->|ServiceMeshMember CRDs| ServiceMeshCP[Service Mesh Control Plane]

    %% Styling
    style RHOAIOperator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Required
    style Kubernetes fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OpenShift fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style PrometheusOp fill:#e6522c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External Optional
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ServiceMesh fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style AddonOperator fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style GitRepo fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal RHOAI Components
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
